{"title":"在北京看雪","authors":["郭文斌"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":12,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北京看雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭文斌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到雪用它的温柔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把树压折"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把灯光压垮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一个人的心压成故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无言的故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在雪中成长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我觉得眼前飘飞的其实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是一群回家的游子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步匆忙得有些跌跌撞撞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同相思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伫立雪中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才明白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪的姿态其实就是相思的姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪的道路其实就是怀念的道路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对这群扑向大地的飞蛾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心是一床翼羽的被子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以她准备了整整一年的盛宴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的盛宴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走失多年的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以一种站着的姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺在这床"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温暖而又寒冷的被子里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我终于看清了雪纷乱的心思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也懂得了雪为什么要以"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种舞蹈的方式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进拥抱"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}